7. function的可选参数设置
'当可选参数有默认值
Function mySum(r as range, Optional useColumn as Boolean = False)
End Function
'当可选参数无默认值,IsMissing只能配合Variant,且可选参数不能有默认值
Function mySum(a, Optional b)
If IsMissing(b) Then
    mySum = a + 1
Else
    mySum = a + b
End Function

